<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078662" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Celeberrimo atque Incomparabili 
                   <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p><rs key="B_1714-08-15_991170515019905501" type="letter">Litteras tuas humanissimas</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Michelotti, 15. August 1714.</note> 15 hujus deficientis Men<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>sis Augusti a Te exaratas ante 8 dies accepi, easque
                   <lb/>Nobilissimo Equiti ac <choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice> Marci Procuratori <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzino</rs>
<lb/>Patavini <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i</rs> Moderatori Amplissimo com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>municavi. Ex ipsius discursu deduxi desiderium,
                   <lb/>Clarissimam ac Doctissimam tuam Personam
                   <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> conducendi, quo capitur; atque insuper
                   <lb/>intellexi illum esse maxime dispositum ad te
                   <lb/>vocandum cum salario, quod petivisti, 1500 Thale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rorum imperialium, hoc est totidem unciarum ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>genti pro quolibet anno. Ipse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me petiit tuarum
                   <lb/>epistolarum copiam<note type="editorial">Gemeint sind die beiden Briefe Bernoullis vom 18. Juli und vom 15. August 1714.</note> ut eas suis sodalibus<note type="editorial"><rs key="pers_DE-588-1111043582" type="person">Alvise Pisani</rs> und <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Francesco Loredan</rs>.</note>
                   Nobilissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mis in <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs> ostenderet, quod factum
                   <lb/>puto. Reliquum igitur est ut sine mora mihi
                   <lb/>rescribas num <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> Patria tua discedes nec ne sala<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rio annuali 1500 Thalerorum imperialium tibi
                   <lb/>persoluto: Si etenim non recusabis rem factam
                   <lb/>esse existimo, et hi <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rendition="#sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell:<hi rendition="#sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Modera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tores</rs> te vocabunt spero, rogabuntque vestrum <rs type="organisation">Ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>gistratum</rs> ut Tibi discessum per aliquot annos <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tria Matheseos edocend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gratia permittat.</p>
<pb facs="1078663" n="1v"/>
<p><lb/>Deprecor et hortor benignitatem tuam ut hoc sala<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rium non recuses: etenim pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terquam quod opti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mum est, progressu temporis poteris (et ego
                   <lb/>coadiuvabo) <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> tuum doctissimum substi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tuere, eique <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> relinquere; ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m
                   <lb/>in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiarum facere oportet de hac re adhoc
                   <lb/>ut Tu Vir Clarissime pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicto salario promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>vearis per aliquot annos. Uti in <rs key="B_1714-08-03_991170515020005501" type="letter">aliis meis episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lis</rs><note type="editorial">siehe z.B. den Brief Michelottis an Johann I Bernoulli vom 3. August 1714: "[...] poteris Venetias te conferre, et in Domo mea habitare absque ullo habitationis, victus, aut alterius rei dispendio; cubile etenim domi me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erit tibi paratum, victum tibi gratis subministrabo, et tota cum libertate poteris mecum commorari;".</note> admonui Domus mea erit pro Te toto vaca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tionum tempore; mihique summi decoris erit Tui
                   <lb/>esse in Mathematiciis (in quibus modice sum exer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>citatus) discipulum. Si salarium 1.500 Tha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lerorum imperialium recusas ambigo quin
                   <lb/>Clarissimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs> tuus, pro quo mea semper
                   <lb/>interponam officia, <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> advocetur.</p>
<p>Tuum igitur per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> expectabo <rs key="B_1714-09-12_991170515019705501" type="letter">responsum</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli antwortet in seinem Brief vom 12. September 1714 an Michelotti.</note>
<lb/>Vir Celeberrime. Interim te admonitum ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lim me accepisse non solum <rs key="B_1714-07-18_991170515020205501" type="letter">tuam epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli hat seinen Brief vom 18. Juli 1714 an Michelotti über Tirol geschickt, in der Hoffnung, dass er dadurch zuverlässiger ankäme.</note>
<lb/>per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> ad me amandatam, ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m etiam
                   <lb/><rs key="B_1714-08-08_991170517053305501" type="letter">eas</rs><note type="editorial">Nikolaus I Bernoulli an Michelotti, 8. August 1714.</note>, quas per <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs> transmisit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs>
<pb facs="1078664" n="2r"/>
<lb/>tuus, quem toto corde <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me salutatum cupio,
                   <lb/>quemque magni facio, et rogo ut mihi parcat
                   <lb/>si epistolis suis mihi carissimis non respondeo;
                   <lb/>plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> enim Nobilium <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>grotantium visitatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nes, quibus quotidi<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> sum oppressus impedimento
                   <lb/>sunt ut plures conscribere possim epistolas.</p>
<p>Fluidorum crassitiem duplici modo considerasti
                   <lb/>quoad densitatem, et quoad consistentiam seu tenaci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tatem; rogo nunc ut Fluidorum crassitiem consi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>deres quoad magnitudinem minimarum particu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>larum fluida coagmentantium; et definias mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>matice annon fluidum illud (tenacitate, et densita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>te non considerabis) dicendum sit crassius, cuius parti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> componentes sunt maiorum diametrorum. Rogo
                   <lb/>ulterius ut mihi indices num tuta sit via mensu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>randi particularum fluida data componentium
                   <lb/>magnitudines ideoque crassitiem et subti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>litatem fluidorum datorum dimetien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>di per filtrationem eorundem fluidorum per po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ros dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> magnitudinis; ita ut si oleum ex. gr. per eos
                   <lb/>poros non transeat, per quos aqua effluit, oleum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
                   <pb facs="1078665" n="2v"/>
<lb/>crassius sit dicendum, idest constare particulis maio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rum diametrorum.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale Vir Amicissime et Celeberrime, et stipen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dium 1500 Thalerorum ne recuses rogo saltem
                   <lb/>adhoc ut progressu temporis promoveatur
                   <lb/>Clarissimus Nepos Tuus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs>.</salute>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice><date when="1714-08-31">31 Augusti 1714.</date></dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>